parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Failure Due to Rusted Brake Lines
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of brake lines due to rust can cause a sudden loss of braking ability, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: brake pedal goes to the floor

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty ABS system can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
The failure of the brake pedal can cause a sudden loss of braking ability, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: brake pedal goes to the floor

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unexpected deployment of the passenger airbag can cause startle, distraction, and potentially lead to accidents, especially if it occurs while the vehicle is in motion. In addition, the deployment can cause injuries to occupants and damage to the vehicle's interior.
symptoms: The passenger airbag deploys suddenly and without warning
often accompanied by a loud noise and a burst of dust or debris. The airbag may deploy while the vehicle is stationary or in motion
and may occur without any apparent reason or trigger.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine compartment fires can cause complete loss of the vehicle, personal belongings, and potentially lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Smoke coming from under the hood
smoke coming through the air vents

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Defective Windshield Wiper Motor Circuit Board
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield wiper motor circuit board can cause the windshield wipers to quit randomly, reducing visibility and increasing the risk of accidents, especially during inclement weather conditions.
symptoms: windshield wipers do not turn on
windshield wipers do not respond to switch input.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunctioning seat belts can increase the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident, as occupants may not be properly restrained.
symptoms: The seat belt will not stay latched
the seat belt will not pull out
difficulty buckling or unbuckling the seat belt.
